</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>疑 Apple 雙插頭充電器諜照曝光，並排雙 USB C 插口及折疊插腳</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/15/appledualoutputcharger/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=appledualoutputcharger</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 15 Apr 2022 05:50:24 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手機配件]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[充電器]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1095307</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>繼早前有消息指 Apple 將推出一款配備雙插口的充電器後，近日網上更流出充電器的實物諜照。 &#160; T [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">繼早前有消息指<a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/04/09/apple-support-doc-reveals-unreleased-dual-usb-c-35w-power-adapter/parts/"> Apple 將推出一款配備雙插口的充電器後</a>，近日網上更流出充電器的實物諜照。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Twitter 用戶 ChargerLAB 在稍早前發表帖文，附上有關充電器的實物圖。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger-694x504.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="504" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger-694x504.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger-1239x900.jpg 1239w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger-768x558.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger-1536x1116.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/charger.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">從照片中可見，充電器貫徹 Apple 一貫的白色簡約設計，附有兩個並排的 USB Type C 插口。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而底部的灰色面上，則配備可折疊收藏的插腳。圖片中的插腳上亦有圓形凹位。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3Iz9aQAUW7ED-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3Iz9aQAUW7ED-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3Iz9aQAUW7ED-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3Iz9aQAUW7ED-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3Iz9aQAUW7ED.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1095315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3I0RXEA05-mM-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3I0RXEA05-mM-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3I0RXEA05-mM-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3I0RXEA05-mM-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/FQG3I0RXEA05-mM.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而早前流出的資料指，插座的輸出功率為 35W，相信主要用於為 iPhone、Apple Watch 及 AirPods 等兩款產品同時充電。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而著名分析師郭明錤亦曾於三月在 Twitter 上發文指，Apple 正在開發一款 30W 充電器，目前接近量產，並會於 2022 年內發佈。隨後他亦有發文，暗示該款產品與傳言中的 35W 充電器相同。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Predicted last month that a new charger of about 30W would come in 2022. Components are nearing mass production, and this year&#39;s shipment estimation could reach 2-3M units.<a href="https://t.co/Xb2keIGYSQ">https://t.co/Xb2keIGYSQ</a></p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1512782073052172288?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 9, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/chargerlab/status/1513692318829727744">Twitter ChargerLAB</a> &amp; <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1512782073052172288?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo)</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
